last_episode_to_air.name: The Deal for Moebius
last_episode_to_air.overview: Su Yeon rushes to the site where the deal is happening to help Chun Woo, who is at risk of being exposed. Meanwhile, Chun Woo does whatever he can to prove his innocence and keep the situation under control when word of a possible rat surfaces. However, all fingers point to him being the rat, making things frustrating and dire.

name: Moebius Project 2012: The Veil
overview: The story of a huge incident faced by Seo Soo-yeon from the support management team that supports and manages NIS field agents in China, Jang Cheon-woo, a hidden NIS black agent and Do Jin-sook, deputy director of overseas parts.

episodes.name: The Drug Deal
episodes.overview: The murder of her sister sets Su Yeon out for vengeance. While she works with Chang Chun Woo, a black agent working undercover in the Samhwa Gang, the man she was after appears in a drug deal. Her desire for revenge overtakes her and puts the operation in jeopardy.
